Navy SEAL Casey Ryback—an error that could be fatal.","genre_ids":[28,53],"popularity":2.8116,"vote_count":1678,"poster_path":"/lQ1SvjOQYLtSeUwcWrzqL0qdRoH.jpg","release_date":"1992-10-08","vote_average":6.295,"backdrop_path":"/ihBDaN7OwT7D9DVri8SmxCnuRLB.jpg","original_title":"Under Siege","original_language":"en"},{"id":9056,"adult":false,"title":"Police Story","video":false,"overview":"Officer Chan Ka Kui manages to put a major Hong Kong drug dealer behind the bars practically alone, after a shooting and an impressive chase inside a slum. Now, he must protect the boss' secretary, Selina, who will testify against the gangster in court.","genre_ids":[28,80,35],"popularity":3.1905,"vote_count":1005,"poster_path":"/1eFB0Iy1TMU4VO5hMcoCE064JAT.jpg","release_date":"1985-12-14","vote_average":7.528,"backdrop_path":"/eYDAnSidN4rIEuneS5gEJkTyk3l.jpg","original_title":"警察故事","original_language":"cn"},{"id":8867,"adult":false,"title":"The Punisher","video":false,"overview":"The avenging angel of Marvel Comics fame comes brilliantly to life in this searing action-adventure thriller! Dolph Lundgren stars as Frank Castle, a veteran cop who loses his entire family to a mafia car bomb. His ex-partner believes Castle survived the blast and became the Punisher, living in the sewers and exacting vigilante violence against mob bosses throughout the city. When the populace is caught in the midst of a gang war that he caused, Castle must again emerge from the shadows and save the innocent.","genre_ids":[28,80,18,53],"popularity":2.1132,"vote_count":653,"poster_path":"/tA0O0hYyHX7Hl2Fl8VEtGtfBtjI.jpg","release_date":"1989-10-05","vote_average":5.768,"backdrop_path":"/tFmrdnfXM0p6ihMTFpptYOKEfSl.jpg","original_title":"The Punisher","original_language":"en"},{"id":9482,"adult":false,"title":"Judge Dredd","video":false,"overview":"In a dystopian future, Dredd, the most famous judge (a cop with instant field judiciary powers) is convicted for a crime he did not commit while his murderous counterpart escapes.","genre_ids":[878,28],"popularity":5.0755,"vote_count":2664,"poster_path":"/cfSnKn8NDU3m8UxihjVcYprA0Aq.jpg","release_date":"1995-06-30","vote_average":5.844,"backdrop_path":"/baJHUXBcoaHnMf2sjwegbuhIjEV.jpg","original_title":"Judge Dredd","original_language":"en"},{"id":9355,"adult":false,"title":"Mad Max Beyond Thunderdome","video":false,"overview":"Mad Max becomes a pawn in a decadent oasis of a technological society, and when exiled, becomes the deliverer of a colony of children.","genre_ids":[28,12,878],"popularity":4.2319,"vote_count":3184,"poster_path":"/jJlxcEVVUHnrUeEkQ0077VeHQpb.jpg","release_date":"1985-06-29","vote_average":6.217,"backdrop_path":"/br1zDvgmBPa1EbBrUmEDaXXgykq.jpg","original_title":"Mad Max Beyond Thunderdome","original_language":"en"},{"id":9387,"adult":false,"title":"Conan the Barbarian","video":false,"overview":"A horde of rampaging warriors massacre the parents of young Conan and enslave the young child for years on The Wheel of Pain. As the sole survivor of the childhood massacre, Conan is released from slavery and taught the ancient arts of fighting. Transforming himself into a killing machine, Conan travels into the wilderness to seek vengeance on Thulsa Doom, the man responsible for killing his family. In the wilderness, Conan takes up with the thieves Valeria and Subotai. The group comes upon King Osric, who wants the trio of warriors to help rescue his daughter who has joined Doom in the hills.","genre_ids":[12,14,28],"popularity":5.9972,"vote_count":2723,"poster_path":"/qw2A587Ee61IwcSOLNFRhuOACZZ.jpg","release_date":"1982-03-16","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/6cYPpzjHcxcSaXEQc8s3sMbcfZS.jpg","original_title":"Conan the Barbarian","original_language":"en"},{"id":9312,"adult":false,"title":"Mortal Kombat","video":false,"overview":"For nine generations an evil sorcerer has been victorious in hand-to-hand battle against his mortal enemies. If he wins a tenth Mortal Kombat tournament, desolation and evil will reign over the multiverse forever. To save Earth, three warriors must overcome seemingly insurmountable odds, their own inner demons, and superhuman foes.","genre_ids":[28,14],"popularity":3.6044,"vote_count":2461,"poster_path":"/fcK7tzSSXMYiMN8E9KlZJL1BYyp.jpg","release_date":"1995-08-18","vote_average":5.874,"backdrop_path":"/dfU9xyEEyLxvZ5unTn05Whm9Lce.jpg","original_title":"Mortal Kombat","original_language":"en"},{"id":9342,"adult":false,"title":"The Mask of Zorro","video":false,"overview":"It has been twenty years since Don Diego de la Vega fought Spanish oppression in Alta California as the legendary romantic hero, Zorro. Having escaped from prison he transforms troubled bandit Alejandro into his successor, in order to foil the plans of the tyrannical Don Rafael Montero who robbed him of his freedom, his wife and his precious daughter.","genre_ids":[28,12],"popularity":4.5061,"vote_count":4255,"poster_path":"/bdMufwGDDzqu4kTSQwrKc5WR4bu.jpg","release_date":"1998-07-16","vote_average":6.577,"backdrop_path":"/wn0e4o0FYd2cBouOviUeTOWzL89.jpg","original_title":"The Mask of Zorro","original_language":"en"},{"id":9425,"adult":false,"title":"Soldier","video":false,"overview":"Sergeant Todd is a veteran soldier for an elite group of the armed forces. After being defeated by a new breed of genetically engineered soldiers, he is dumped on a waste planet and left for dead. He soon interacts with a group of crash survivors who lead out a peaceful existence. The peace is broken as the new soldiers land on the planet to eliminate the colony, which Sergeant Todd must defend.","genre_ids":[878,28,18],"popularity":1.7892,"vote_count":911,"poster_path":"/rYy5m4nnjdlvB6dyGkP9ELZbUZz.jpg","release_date":"1998-10-23","vote_average":6.4,"backdrop_path":"/eYrjffVvcc0MEgy9RcquvWyBGtQ.jpg","original_title":"Soldier","original_language":"en"},{"id":278540,"adult":false,"title":"Girl's Blood","video":false,"overview":"Four girls take part in illegal underground fighting event \"Girl's Blood\" held at an abandoned school building in Roppongi every night. The girls have their own stories and quirks from their private lives. Satsuki (Yuria Haga) suffers from a gender identity disorder, Chinatsu (Asami Tada) ran away from an abusive husband, Miko (Ayame Misaki) is a S&amp;M queen and Mayu (Rina Koike) has a Lolita face.","genre_ids":[28,18,10749],"popularity":4.7693,"vote_count":36,"poster_path":"/9Oc7cqHsPLA1FvNLmF6jUAz38tg.jpg","release_date":"2014-02-22","vote_average":6.139,"backdrop_path":"/kB2DXsW4QZP33Skch3pE0ZCPThj.jpg","original_title":"赤×ピンク","original_language":"ja"},{"id":9462,"adult":false,"title":"The Way of the Dragon","video":false,"overview":"After a Chinese restaurant in Rome is threatened by the mafia, who will stop at nothing to acquire the property, the owner recruits a family friend in Hong Kong, kung fu expert Tang Lung, to help them defend their business.","genre_ids":[28,80],"popularity":5.2953,"vote_count":1243,"poster_path":"/m7AIITQ624sfldI4SsX4htXPH1f.jpg","release_date":"1972-12-30","vote_average":7.367,"backdrop_path":"/hQaYzVQGwLK04TgTiQkJB9lHmY8.jpg","original_title":"猛龍過江","original_language":"cn"},{"id":9334,"adult":false,"title":"The Scorpion King","video":false,"overview":"In ancient Egypt, peasant Mathayus is hired to exact revenge on the powerful Memnon and the sorceress Cassandra, who are ready to overtake Balthazar's village. Amid betrayals, thieves, abductions and more, Mathayus strives to bring justice to his complicated world.","genre_ids":[28,12,14],"popularity":5.4578,"vote_count":3319,"poster_path":"/aITIsX20tACn6jgtyDcCYpRT216.jpg","release_date":"2002-04-18","vote_average":5.593,"backdrop_path":"/nZSUgauXlVUrJGdGUGWMXCtnZx4.jpg","original_title":"The Scorpion King","original_language":"en"},{"id":9335,"adult":false,"title":"Transporter 2","video":false,"overview":"Professional driver, and former Special Forces officer, Frank Martin is living in Miami, where he is temporarily filling in for a friend 